ot i \u00e5 handle ny veteranbil. Men n\u00e5 har han lovet madammen \u00e5 trappe ned.", "Men det var etter dette at han anskaffet Buicken og Impalaen - for \u00e5 tr\u00f8ste seg selv etter salget av den \u00e5pne Buicken . . ."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "bil"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "bil|veteran"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "b5431d1b5a1c92f51fe3e59c48c0d97851bb7ad2f6e42c1714a38e9950f4ae4f"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T09:19:10.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Jann St\u00f8vereide har en imponerende stall av veterankj\u00f8ret\u00f8yer. Men favoritten er en 1946 Chevrolet lastebil."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1200173.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/36Chev2"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/bd400d4a679b304a9eec92200b8a8964c36c39d3.jpg?598df327"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Lastebiler er det gjeveste -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "bd400d4a679b304a9eec92200b8a8964c36c39d3"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim", "ukeadressa", "eadressa", "skattelister", "d\u00f8dsfall", "tr\u00f8nder", "trafikk"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "nyheter,trondheim,ukeadressa,eadressa,skattelister,d\u00f8dsfall,tr\u00f8nder,trafikk"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["bil", "veteran"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "automotive"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "chevrolet"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["bil", "lastebil", "kj\u00f8re"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["chrysler", "buicken og impalaen", "chevroleten", "vestlandet", "lars", "jann", "buicken", "buick convertible phaeton", "\u00e5heim"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["sunnm\u00f8re", "fargo"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["